Everything is fine. There is no danger -- Veniamin Kondratyev: During the night, the Tikhoretsk district was subjected to a terrorist attack by the Kyiv regime. Two drones were suppressed by air defense and electronic warfare systems. Due to the fall of debris from one of them, a fire broke out, spreading to explosive objects. Detonation began.
